title: Katherine Ryan: A Joke about Her Contractor
description: Katherine Ryan jokes about her contractor in her Netflix special, "Glitter Room". Grab your tickets at NetflixIsAJokeFest.com to see Katherine and your other favorite comedians in the Netflix is a Joke Fest happening April 28th-May 8th in Los Angeles.
